  "3316960": {
    "name": "Ashes of Morgravia",
    "steam_appid": 3316960,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316960/extras/27a90f4efe5cccaacb5524b0615a561a.poster.avif?t=1770243151\" width=856 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316960/extras/27a90f4efe5cccaacb5524b0615a561a.webm?t=1770243151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Ashes of Morgravia</i> 是一款<strong>策略卡牌构筑游戏</strong>，背景设定在一个阴沉衰败的世界中，在这里，众神陨落，人类在其毁灭的阴影下挣扎求生.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凭借独特的<strong>双牌系统</strong>、<strong>基于卡牌的策略战斗</strong>以及充满氛围的<strong>暗黑幻想</strong>设定，<i>Ashes of Morgravia</i>挑战玩家穿越被漫漫黑夜笼罩的废墟，直面那些无情、充斥着坏死能量的恐怖生物.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316960/extras/f7b24eeaff8809007fa6af7fc3fc6f1b.avif?t=1770243151\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316960/extras_big/f7b24eeaff8809007fa6af7fc3fc6f1b.avif?t=1770243151 width=800 height=157 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>双牌系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握两副独特的牌组——一副用于移动，另一副用于战斗。在这个充满动态变化的卡牌系统中，穿越险恶地形，与敌人激烈交锋.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316960/extras/8a9bc53120af446ed0b6ffc253d8468b.poster.avif?t=1770243151\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316960/extras/8a9bc53120af446ed0b6ffc253d8468b.webm?t=1770243151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>动画卡牌</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在全动画的卡牌中，让每个动作焕发生命力.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316960/extras/95fa07f10e8a9e618fb9926bcb40e6fd.poster.avif?t=1770243151\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316960/extras/95fa07f10e8a9e618fb9926bcb40e6fd.webm?t=1770243151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战术定位</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精心规划你的每一步。使用如<i>Relocate</i>这样的卡牌，穿梭于战场之中，智取你的敌人.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316960/extras/5d2023b13cbb71179e3da22ba16a4879.poster.avif?t=1770243151\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316960/extras/5d2023b13cbb71179e3da22ba16a4879.webm?t=1770243151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>严峻的敌人</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直面被坏死能量扭曲的恐怖生物，每场战斗都迫使你调整策略以应对不断变化的挑战.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316960/extras/a44dc8ea6205163e909d59dceb5ee6fb.poster.avif?t=1770243151\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316960/extras/a44dc8ea6205163e909d59dceb5ee6fb.webm?t=1770243151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自定义与进阶</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集遗物、神圣残骸和强力装备，升级你的技能，为自己在这黑暗而危险的世界中开辟一条前行之路.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316960/extras/6b1b960c14f6c2f69222291d2be10b99.poster.avif?t=1770243151\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316960/extras/6b1b960c14f6c2f69222291d2be10b99.webm?t=1770243151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>命运的抉择</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >邂逅尘封的往昔遗迹，做出将决定你旅途和命运的关键抉择.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316960/extras/e74eee251236941629e0bdf5d1a50777.poster.avif?t=1770243151\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316960/extras/e74eee251236941629e0bdf5d1a50777.webm?t=1770243151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>独特的艺术风格</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >视觉设计体现了<i>Ashes of Morgravia</i>核心的二元对立——神圣与亵渎、光明与黑暗、秩序与混沌。采用金色与蓝色为主的调色板，游戏将玩家带入一个鲜明对比构筑其世界、其<strong>受膏者</strong>以及敌人的境界.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>沉浸式暗黑幻想世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上莫格拉维亚永恒黑夜之旅，这里大地留下了神圣战役与坏死腐蚀的痕迹。在探索充满传奇色彩的世界时，解开众神陨落之谜.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316960/extras/3befa58e7937847b55cb92bc9f73408b.poster.avif?t=1770243151\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316960/extras/3befa58e7937847b55cb92bc9f73408b.webm?t=1770243151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316960/extras/3befa58e7937847b55cb92bc9f73408b.mp4?t=1770243151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>灵感源自顶尖的卡牌构筑与暗黑幻想作品</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你曾为那些定义了卡牌构筑流派的<i><strong>游戏</strong></i>或俯视视角RPG的策略深度所折服，<i>Ashes of Morgravia</i>将以其独特的卡牌构筑机制与战术玩法深深吸引你.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏设定在一个暗黑幻想世界中，让人联想到启发出souls-like流派的那些作品。在这里，腐朽的神祇俯视着破败的景观，而神圣冲突的残余则塑造着每一次遭遇.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索由破碎神殿、庞大陨落的神明和怪诞敌人构成的世界，同时做出生死攸关的抉择，为你的命运定下基调.</p>",
